quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  22,73,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, misal piyaama jentee ngal, pellet …ìen …ìe noddoton gaanin Alla, …ìe tagaa hay coongil, hay sinndo …ìe moo…ìondiriino fii …óum. Si coongil(mbuubu)ngil jattii …ìe go…ó…óum …ìe hattantaake ja…ìtugol ngil …óum. ∆äa…ì…ìu…óo on e …óa…ì…ìaa…óo on fow no lo'i"
  22,74,"∆Åe mawniniraali Alla no O haani Mawninirde non. Pellet, Alla ko O Dolnu…óo Teddu…óo"
  22,75,"Alla no su…ìoo immorde e Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen Nulaa…ìe e yim…ìe …ìen kadi. Pellet, Alla ko O Nanoowo Yi'oowo"
  22,76,"Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso ma…ì…ìe e ko woni kon hedde …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, ko faade ka Alla fiyakuuji …óin ruttetee"
  22,77,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óin…ìe, Ru∆¥∆¥ee Sujjon Rewon Joomi mo'on, gollon ko mo∆¥∆¥i kon belajo'o onon on maloyte"
  22,78,"Wa…óiree Jihaadi fii Alla no Jihaadi haaniri non, Kanko O Su…ìike on O wa…óanaali on …ìitteende ka nder Diina, Diina baaba moo…óon Ibraahiima ko Kanko inni on jul…ìe ko adii [ndee Alqur'aanaare] e nder mayre kadi, fii yo Nulaa…óo on laato seedo e hoore-mo'on onon kadi wonon seeditoytoo…ìe e hoore yim…ìe …ìen. √ëii…ìnee e Julde nden totton Jakka on jogitee Alla, ko Kanko woni Gi…óo moo…óon mo∆¥∆¥ii gi…óo mo∆¥∆¥ii walloowo on"
